        public BuiltFile skip(int number)
        The number of objects to skip before returning any.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        BuiltFile object, so you can chain this call.

        Note :- You can use this method to add constraint in fetchAll(BuiltFilesResultCallback), fetchImages(BuiltFilesResultCallback) and fetchVideos(BuiltFilesResultCallback) methods.

      • includeCount

        public BuiltFile includeCount()
        Retrieve count and data of objects in result.
        Returns:
        BuiltFile object, so you can chain this call.

      • Call getCount() method in the success to get count of objects.
